# Cursor Debug Rules v1 (Not Implemented Yet)

## Debugging Process
1. Reproduce the issue
2. Add logging/debugging statements
3. Isolate the problem
4. Fix the root cause
5. Add tests to prevent regression

## Debugging Tools
- Python debugger (pdb)
- Logging statements
- Print statements (temporary)
- Error tracking (Sentry)

## Best Practices
- Understand the problem before fixing
- Test the fix thoroughly
- Document the solution
- Learn from the issue
